reshist_addr3_coi_zed_apenr.Description: Educational Domain Advanced Placement course enrollment: Ratio of students enrolled in at least one AP course to the number of 11th and 12th graders, transformed to z-scores.

reshist_addr3_coi_zed_attain.Description: Educational Domain Adult educational attainment: Percentage adults ages 25 and over with a college degree or higher, transformed to z-scores.

reshist_addr3_coi_zed_college.Description: Educational Domain College enrollment in nearby institutions: Percentage 18-24 year-olds enrolled in college within 25-mile radius, transformed to z-scores.

reshist_addr3_coi_zed_ecenrol.Description: Educational Domain Early childhood education enrollment Percentage 3- and 4-year-olds enrolled in nursery school, preschool or kindergarten, transformed to z-scores.

reshist_addr3_coi_zed_hsgrad.Description: Educational Domain High school graduation rate: Percentage ninth graders graduating from high school on time, transformed to z-scores.

reshist_addr3_coi_zed_math.Description: Educational Domain Third grade math proficiency: Percentage third graders scoring proficient on standardized math tests, converted to NAEP scale score points, transformed to z-scores.

reshist_addr3_coi_zed_reading.Description: Educational Domain Third grade reading proficiency: Percentage third graders scoring proficient on standardized reading tests, converted to NAEP scale score points, transformed to z-scores.

reshist_addr3_coi_zed_schpov.Description: Educational Domain Teacher experience: Percentage students in elementary schools eligible for free or reduced-price lunches, transformed to z-scores and multiplied by -1.

reshist_addr3_coi_zed_teachxp.Description: Educational Domain Teacher Experience: Percentage teachers in their first and second year, transformed to z-scores and multiplied by -1.

reshist_addr3_coi_zed_prxece.Description: Educational Domain Early childhood education centers: Number of ECE centers within a 5-mile radius, converted to natural log units, transformed to z-scores.

reshist_addr3_coi_zed_prxhqece.Description: Educational Domain High-quality early childhood education centers: Number of NAEYC accredited centers within a 5-mile radius, converted to natural log units, transformed to z-scores.

reshist_addr3_coi_zhe_food.Description: Health and Environment Domain Access to healthy food: Percentage households without a car located further than a half-mile from the nearest supermarket, transformed to z-scores and multiplied by -1.

reshist_addr3_coi_zhe_green.Description: Health and Environment Domain Access to green space: Percentage impenetrable surface areas such as rooftops, roads or parking lots, transformed to z-scores and multiplied by -1.

reshist_addr3_coi_zhe_heat.Description: Health and Environment Domain Extreme heat exposure: Summer days with maximum temperature above 90F, transformed to z-scores and multiplied by -1.

reshist_addr3_coi_zhe_hlthins.Description: Health and Environment Domain Health insurance coverage: Percentage individuals ages 0-64 with health insurance coverage, transformed to z-scores.

reshist_addr3_coi_zhe_ozone.Description: Health and Environment Domain Ozone concentration: Mean estimated 8-hour average ozone concentration, transformed to z-scores and multiplied by -1.

reshist_addr3_coi_zhe_pm25.Description: Health and Environment Domain Airborne microparticles: Mean estimated microparticle (PM2.5) concentration, transformed to z-scores and multiplied by -1.

reshist_addr3_coi_zhe_vacancy.Description: Health and Environment Domain Housing Vacancy Rate: Percentage housing units that are vacant, transformed to z-scores and multiplied by -1.

reshist_addr3_coi_zhe_walk.Description: Health and Environment Domain Walkability: EPA Walkability Index, transformed to z-scores.

reshist_addr3_coi_zhe_suprfnd.Description: Health and Environment Domain Industrial pollutants in air, water or soil: Average number of Superfund sites within a 2-mile radius, converted to natural log units, transformed to z-scores and multiplied by -1.

reshist_addr3_coi_zhe_rsei.Description: Health and Environment Domain Industrial pollutants Industrial pollutants in air, water or soil: Index of toxic chemicals released by industrial facilities, converted to natural log units, transformed to z-scores and multiplied by -1.

reshist_addr3_coi_zse_povrate.Description: Social and Economic Domain: Poverty rate z-score

reshist_addr3_coi_zse_public.Description: Social and Economic Domain: Public assistance rate z-score

reshist_addr3_coi_zse_home.Description: Social and Economic Domain: Homeownership rate z-score

reshist_addr3_coi_zse_occ.Description: Social and Economic Domain: High-skill employment z-score

reshist_addr3_coi_zse_mhe.Description: Social and Economic Domain: Median household income z-score

reshist_addr3_coi_zse_emprat.Description: Employment rate: Percentage adults ages 25-54 who are employed, transformed to z-scores.

reshist_addr3_coi_zse_jobprox.Description: Commute duration: Percentage workers commuting more than one hour one way, transformed to z-scores and multiplied by -1.

reshist_addr3_coi_zse_single.Description: Single-headed households: Percentage family households that are single-parent headed, transformed to z-scores and multiplied by -1.

reshist_addr3_coi_zse_ecres.Description: Economic resource index: combines poverty rate, public assistance rate, homeownership rate, high skill employment, and median household income, transformed to z-scores.

reshist_addr1_coi_z_ed_nat.Description: Z-scores, education domain, nationally-normed: Weighted average of education domain component indicator z-scores, nationally normed.

reshist_addr1_coi_z_he_nat.Description: Z-scores, health and environment domain, nationally-normed: Weighted average of health and environment domain component indicator z-scores, nationally normed.

reshist_addr1_coi_z_se_nat.Description: Z-scores, social and economic domain, nationally-normed: Weighted average of social and economic domain component indicator z-scores, nationally normed.
